% <include>context/python_preamble.prompt</include>

% Goal
Write the `pdd/agentic_common.py` module.

% Role & Scope
Shared infrastructure for agentic CLI invocations (Claude Code, Gemini, Codex). Provides reusable utilities for agent discovery, environment sanitization, logging, and subprocess orchestration. This module acts as the low-level interface between PDD orchestrators and external agentic CLIs, handling provider-specific JSON parsing, cost calculation, and state persistence.

